00:14:52,540 --> 00:14:54,000
I've finally found you.

283
00:15:02,300 --> 00:15:04,450
So this... This is your-

284
00:15:04,510 --> 00:15:05,030
You two-

285
00:15:05,030 --> 00:15:06,550
He's a weapon spirit, named Xiu.

286
00:15:09,500 --> 00:15:10,740
Oh, so he's a weapon spirit.

287
00:15:10,940 --> 00:15:12,490
Looks quite cute.

288
00:15:12,840 --> 00:15:13,550
How did you think of

289
00:15:13,550 --> 00:15:14,490
coming to Yandu to find me?

290
00:15:14,630 --> 00:15:16,120
I originally came down the mountain

291
00:15:16,230 --> 00:15:18,080
to find a place for cultivation.

292
00:15:18,080 --> 00:15:18,750
But unexpectedly,

293
00:15:18,750 --> 00:15:20,120
I ran into Zi Fei and the others on the way.

294
00:15:20,120 --> 00:15:21,600
That guy asked me to come help you.

295
00:15:21,600 --> 00:15:22,390
He said when he left,

296
00:15:22,390 --> 00:15:23,550
he didn't leave you enough money,

297
00:15:23,670 --> 00:15:24,790
so he asked me to bring you some.

298
00:15:25,790 --> 00:15:27,440
That's really kind of you. Thank you so much.

299
00:15:27,720 --> 00:15:28,910
Now that we have money,

300
00:15:29,150 --> 00:15:30,540
Xiu can finally eat his fill.

301
00:15:33,240 --> 00:15:34,350
How did you find me?

302
00:15:34,840 --> 00:15:36,240
How did I find you?

303
00:15:36,240 --> 00:15:38,030
I've been wandering around the city for several days.

304
00:15:38,030 --> 00:15:38,720
I just ran into

305
00:15:38,720 --> 00:15:39,620
this child on the road.

306
00:15:39,640 --> 00:15:40,240
Right,

307
00:15:40,320 --> 00:15:41,390
I smelled your scent on him.

308
00:15:41,390 --> 00:15:42,420
I followed the scent all the way here.

309
00:15:43,200 --> 00:15:44,630
What a dog nose you have.

310
00:15:47,210 --> 00:15:48,020
Xiu!

311
00:15:48,080 --> 00:15:48,840
Xiu!

312
00:15:52,720 --> 00:15:53,360
He ran away?

313
00:15:54,320 --> 00:15:55,120
Xiu!

314
00:15:57,910 --> 00:15:58,790
Whose child is this?

315
00:15:58,790 --> 00:15:59,750
I'm sorry.

316
00:16:00,080 --> 00:16:00,790
Xiu!

317
00:16:00,790 --> 00:16:01,790
What's going on?

318
00:16:01,790 --> 00:16:02,600
Xiu!

319
00:16:05,790 --> 00:16:06,480
My wine!

320
00:16:06,480 --> 00:16:07,270
You've caused trouble again.

321
00:16:07,270 --> 00:16:08,000
Pay for it!

322
00:16:08,000 --> 00:16:09,080
I'm sorry, I'm sorry.

323
00:16:09,120 --> 00:16:10,360
I'll compensate you.

324
00:16:11,040 --> 00:16:12,350
Quick, give me the money pouch.

325
00:16:14,550 --> 00:16:15,360
It's gone.

326
00:16:16,840 --> 00:16:18,240
Xiu, spit it out now.

327
00:16:18,720 --> 00:16:19,440
Xiu, listen to me.

328
00:16:19,440 --> 00:16:20,600
Spit it out right now. Be a good boy.

329
00:16:20,620 --> 00:16:21,660
Or I'll have to spank you.

330
00:16:24,080 --> 00:16:25,440
This little guy has really caused trouble.

331
00:16:25,440 --> 00:16:29,360
Yeah, what kind of upbringing is this?

332
00:16:31,120 --> 00:16:32,110
Let me tell you something.

333
00:16:32,110 --> 00:16:33,440
You can't just eat without growing taller.

334
00:16:33,440 --> 00:16:34,240
You understand?

335
00:16:34,360 --> 00:16:35,720
You need to grow up quickly.

336
00:16:37,670 --> 00:16:38,610
Here, this is for you.

337
00:16:42,000 --> 00:16:43,270
This isn't for eating.

338
00:16:43,870 --> 00:16:45,120
This is for playing with.

339
00:16:45,120 --> 00:16:46,690
It's not made of gold, you know?

340
00:17:01,370 --> 00:17:02,300
Yuanzhong, look.

341
00:17:05,640 --> 00:17:06,440
Yuanzhong.

342
00:17:08,720 --> 00:17:09,510
Yuanzhong?

343
00:17:21,480 --> 00:17:22,270
Oh, right.

344
00:17:22,440 --> 00:17:23,839
Zi Fei asked me to pass on a message to you.

345
00:17:24,589 --> 00:17:25,680
He said that after they break Ling Yao's

346
00:17:25,680 --> 00:17:26,640
seal,

347
00:17:26,640 --> 00:17:28,069
they'll go to the Five Extremities on their own.

348
00:17:28,200 --> 00:17:29,480
They won't come to meet you.

349
00:17:30,960 --> 00:17:32,960
But even if they didn't come,

350
00:17:33,380 --> 00:17:34,340
I had to come see you.

351
00:17:35,310 --> 00:17:36,070
Otherwise, next time,

352
00:17:36,070 --> 00:17:36,990
I might not see you again.

353
00:17:40,490 --> 00:17:42,090
When little Xiu grows up,

354
00:17:42,750 --> 00:17:44,030
you'll begin, right?

355
00:17:45,960 --> 00:17:46,750
Yuanzhong.

356
00:17:47,480 --> 00:17:48,540
Have you really made up your mind?

357
00:18:10,900 --> 00:18:12,820
Sir, what would you like to eat?

358
00:18:13,270 --> 00:18:14,160
Same as them.

359
00:18:14,160 --> 00:18:14,880
Got it.

360
00:18:27,270 --> 00:18:29,120
Darling, I'm back.

361
00:18:53,310 --> 00:18:54,680
Why haven't you come home so late?

362
00:18:54,720 --> 00:18:56,160
Xiu is already asleep.

363
00:18:57,500 --> 00:18:59,740
I couldn't sleep, so I came out to find something to eat.

364
00:19:00,920 --> 00:19:01,640
At this hour,

365
00:19:01,640 --> 00:19:03,070
there are still so many customers here.

366
00:19:03,750 --> 00:19:04,550
Yes.

367
00:19:05,200 --> 00:19:06,640
The proprietress has been busy without a break.

368
00:19:07,750 --> 00:19:09,750
This is the unique hustle and bustle of Yandu.

369
00:19:10,590 --> 00:19:12,400
Madam, a bowl of wontons, please.

370
00:19:12,400 --> 00:19:12,980
Sure.

371
00:19:19,880 --> 00:19:21,160
What's wrong? You're not talking.

372
00:19:23,110 --> 00:19:24,440
This place is quite nice.

373
00:19:24,880 --> 00:19:26,000
You have a great eye for picking places.

374
00:19:27,460 --> 00:19:28,030
Is that so?

375
00:19:29,200 --> 00:19:30,750
I've been sitting here for three quarters of an hour,

376
00:19:31,110 --> 00:19:32,420
and the proprietress has been busy for three quarters of an hour.

377
00:19:33,110 --> 00:19:34,310
During this time,

378
00:19:34,310 --> 00:19:35,270
her baby in the cradle

379
00:19:35,270 --> 00:19:36,310
cried twice,

380
00:19:36,400 --> 00:19:37,400
and the slightly older child

381
00:19:37,400 --> 00:19:38,550
broke a bowl.

382
00:19:38,680 --> 00:19:40,240
The proprietress has been so busy that she hasn't had a moment to rest.

383
00:19:40,310 --> 00:19:41,920
She's been tending to the children while running the business,

384
00:19:42,200 --> 00:19:43,160
and hasn't stopped to rest

385
00:19:43,160 --> 00:19:44,160
for even a moment.

386
00:19:45,200 --> 00:19:46,110
Her husband

387
00:19:46,440 --> 00:19:47,750
came back reeking of alcohol,

388
00:19:48,240 --> 00:19:49,200
not only refusing to help,

389
00:19:49,640 --> 00:19:51,200
but nearly overturning the stall.

390
00:19:51,480 --> 00:19:53,000
He looks like a leisurely customer,

391
00:19:53,400 --> 00:19:54,070
acting absolutely not

392
00:19:54,070 --> 00:19:54,880
like he should

393
00:19:54,880 --> 00:19:55,960
as the man of the house.

394
00:19:56,240 --> 00:19:57,960
All these trivial matters

395
00:19:58,110 --> 00:19:59,110
are enough to weigh her down,

396
00:19:59,110 --> 00:20:00,070
leaving her no peace.

397
00:20:00,880 --> 00:20:03,000
Well, I think many things

398
00:20:03,000 --> 00:20:04,400
can't be judged at first glance.

399
00:20:04,680 --> 00:20:06,030
Look at this husband.

400
00:20:06,400 --> 00:20:08,640
Although his clothes are old and worn,

401
00:20:08,750 --> 00:20:09,830
even patched up,

402
00:20:09,880 --> 00:20:10,640
his wife

403
00:20:10,640 --> 00:20:11,960
and the two children's clothes

404
00:20:11,960 --> 00:20:13,720
look much newer in comparison.

405
00:20:14,090 --> 00:20:14,850
His feet

406
00:20:14,880 --> 00:20:16,320
are covered in mud and water,

407
00:20:16,590 --> 00:20:18,310
and his whole body is covered in dust.

408
00:20:18,750 --> 00:20:19,830
He looks like

409
00:20:19,830 --> 00:20:20,880
someone who does hard labor.

410
00:20:21,440 --> 00:20:23,160
Although he smells of alcohol,

411
00:20:23,480 --> 00:20:24,790
it seems

412
00:20:25,640 --> 00:20:27,200
more like medicinal wine.

413
00:20:27,350 --> 00:20:28,110
Perhaps he

414
00:20:28,110 --> 00:20:29,680
finished a hard day's work,

415
00:20:29,680 --> 00:20:30,680
applied some medicinal wine,

416
00:20:30,680 --> 00:20:31,680
and due to exhaustion,

417
00:20:31,850 --> 00:20:33,040
he fell asleep.

418
00:20:33,790 --> 00:20:35,480
You always find a way

419
00:20:35,960 --> 00:20:37,790
to see the better side of things.

420
00:20:38,350 --> 00:20:39,680
Because even though there are

421
00:20:39,680 --> 00:20:40,750
many bad people in this world,

422
00:20:40,830 --> 00:20:42,440
there are also plenty of good ones.

423
00:20:44,720 --> 00:20:45,510
Madam.

424
00:20:45,920 --> 00:20:46,720
Coming.

425
00:20:49,510 --> 00:20:50,720
Business is really good, isn't it?

426
00:20:51,310 --> 00:20:52,720
It's always busiest at this time of day.

427
00:20:52,720 --> 00:20:54,000
The craftsmen from the workshops finish their work,

428
00:20:54,000 --> 00:20:54,640
and they come straight here

429
00:20:54,640 --> 00:20:55,720
for some warm food.

430
00:20:55,880 --> 00:20:57,240
Is that your husband?

431
00:20:57,510 --> 00:20:58,400
Why does he let you

432
00:20:58,400 --> 00:20:59,550
work so hard all by yourself?

433
00:20:59,720 --> 00:21:01,640
Oh, him? He's exhausted from working all day.

434
00:21:01,640 --> 00:21:02,590
I asked him to go home and get some good rest,

435
00:21:02,590 --> 00:21:03,310
but he wouldn't.

436
00:21:03,310 --> 00:21:04,550
He insisted on coming here to keep me company,

437
00:21:04,680 --> 00:21:05,750
so that we could close up later together

438
00:21:05,750 --> 00:21:06,830
and go home together.

439
00:21:09,240 --> 00:21:10,160
You see?

440
00:21:10,400 --> 00:21:11,960
Instead of guessing back and forth here,

441
00:21:11,960 --> 00:21:13,030
worrying yourself,

442
00:21:13,110 --> 00:21:14,960
why don't you just ask directly?

443
00:21:15,270 --> 00:21:16,200
Their life

444
00:21:16,200 --> 00:21:17,350
isn't as bad as you thought,

445
00:21:17,350 --> 00:21:18,160
right?

446
00:21:18,830 --> 00:21:20,270
The couple is loving,

447
00:21:20,440 --> 00:21:22,160
and the family is harmonious.

448
00:21:24,270 --> 00:21:25,070
So,

449
00:21:25,480 --> 00:21:26,640
what's really bothering you?

450
00:21:29,000 --> 00:21:30,750
Ever since we entered Yandu City,

451
00:21:31,550 --> 00:21:33,200
you've been preoccupied

452
00:21:33,240 --> 00:21:34,400
and gloomy.

453
00:21:35,310 --> 00:21:36,640
Is there something on your mind?

454
00:21:39,550 --> 00:21:40,920
Do you believe in fate?

455
00:21:41,750 --> 00:21:42,680
Fate?

456
00:21:44,400 --> 00:21:45,400
When I was born,

457
00:21:45,790 --> 00:21:46,750
the Elders of my clan

458
00:21:46,750 --> 00:21:47,750
read my fortune.

459
00:21:48,160 --> 00:21:50,330
They said my life is cursed by the Seven Killings,

460
00:21:50,480 --> 00:21:51,790
and I'm destined to encounter entanglements.

461
00:21:51,790 --> 00:21:53,200
My life would be turbulent

462
00:21:53,510 --> 00:21:54,640
and full of dangers.

463
00:21:54,960 --> 00:21:56,160
If I focus on doing good,

464
00:21:56,440 --> 00:21:57,830
perhaps in desperate situations,

465
00:21:57,880 --> 00:21:59,270
I might glimpse a chance for survival.

466
00:21:59,920 --> 00:22:02,480
But I must never give in to greed or attachment.

467
00:22:02,830 --> 00:22:03,920
Once I desire something,

468
00:22:04,240 --> 00:22:05,310
that chance for survival will vanish,

469
00:22:05,680 --> 00:22:07,400
and even greater misfortune will follow.

470
00:22:08,960 --> 00:22:09,750
Ji Tanyin.

471
00:22:10,240 --> 00:22:11,160
Don't always try

472
00:22:11,160 --> 00:22:12,270
to probe into others' minds

473
00:22:12,270 --> 00:22:13,510
to figure out what they're really thinking.

474
00:22:14,640 --> 00:22:15,440
After all,

475
00:22:16,230 --> 00:22:17,920
you're not exactly an honest person yourself.

476
00:23:15,750 --> 00:23:16,550
Ji Tanyin.

477
00:23:16,960 --> 00:23:17,880
Don't always try

478
00:23:17,880 --> 00:23:19,070
to probe into others' minds

479
00:23:19,070 --> 00:23:20,310
to figure out what they're really thinking.

480
00:23:20,440 --> 00:23:21,240
After all,

481
00:23:21,550 --> 00:23:23,240
you're not exactly an honest person yourself.

482
00:23:47,450 --> 00:23:51,030
[Dengyun House]

483
00:23:53,200 --> 00:23:56,340
[Painter, Fu Jiuyun]

484
00:24:28,200 --> 00:24:29,000
Xue.

485
00:24:29,830 --> 00:24:30,960
I bought you some treats.

486
00:24:30,960 --> 00:24:31,590
What?

487
00:24:31,880 --> 00:24:33,070
You bought me treats?

488
00:24:33,440 --> 00:24:34,410
What kind of treats?

489
00:24:34,480 --> 00:24:35,350
The sweet cake.

490
00:24:35,960 --> 00:24:37,390
I love that sweet cake.

491
00:24:37,750 --> 00:24:39,510
And this, plum wine.

492
00:24:39,920 --> 00:24:40,680
I'm afraid of getting drunk,

493
00:24:40,680 --> 00:24:41,680
so I've never dared to try it.

494
00:24:41,830 --> 00:24:43,610
It won't make you drunk. It's sweet.

495
00:24:43,630 --> 00:24:44,760
You'll definitely like it.

496
00:24:48,880 --> 00:24:49,880
Where's Qian Lin?

497
00:24:50,400 --> 00:24:52,480
Oh, him? He sleeps all day,

498
00:24:52,480 --> 00:24:53,880
hiding under the blanket, refusing to go out.

499
00:24:54,110 --> 00:24:55,030
I think

500
00:24:55,230 --> 00:24:56,880
he doesn't want me to go in and check on him.

501
00:24:57,880 --> 00:24:58,860
Does he eat?

502
00:24:59,310 --> 00:25:01,400
Yes, he eats everything I bring in.

503
00:25:01,400 --> 00:25:02,480
He eats as much as I bring,

504
00:25:02,480 --> 00:25:03,710
like he's a reincarnated hungry ghost or something.

505
00:25:04,750 --> 00:25:05,720
Thank you for everything.

506
00:25:06,070 --> 00:25:07,000
Don't mention it.

507
00:25:39,510 --> 00:25:40,350
You're awake.

508
00:25:41,750 --> 00:25:42,440
I've prepared

509
00:25:42,440 --> 00:25:43,640
some pastries for you.

510
00:25:43,710 --> 00:25:44,790
Come and try some.

511
00:25:51,070 --> 00:25:52,400
Why did you fall asleep here?

512
00:25:53,400 --> 00:25:54,960
Maybe I've been too tired lately.

513
00:25:56,610 --> 00:25:58,850
Did you have a fight with the High Priest?

514
00:25:59,550 --> 00:26:02,950
He seems to dislike me a bit lately.

515
00:26:03,310 --> 00:26:04,110
Why?

516
00:26:05,030 --> 00:26:06,750
Maybe because he thinks I'm not honest.

517
00:26:08,880 --> 00:26:10,030
Is he honest?

518
00:26:11,920 --> 00:26:12,920
Not really.

519
00:26:14,440 --> 00:26:15,830
Then he's no better than you.

520
00:26:15,830 --> 00:26:17,000
What right does he have to dislike you?

521
00:26:18,880 --> 00:26:19,830
It's different.

522
00:26:20,110 --> 00:26:21,400
Although he's not honest,

523
00:26:21,590 --> 00:26:23,440
I know everything about him.

524
00:26:24,270 --> 00:26:25,310
You know everything?

525
00:26:27,830 --> 00:26:28,960
I doubt that.

526
00:26:32,720 --> 00:26:34,070
Your magic source is broken?

527
00:26:37,480 --> 00:26:38,270
Yes.

528
00:26:39,920 --> 00:26:40,880
It's not a big deal.

529
00:26:41,790 --> 00:26:43,200
Being an ordinary person is quite good.

530
00:26:53,160 --> 00:26:54,240
I'll head back first.

531
00:26:55,350 --> 00:26:56,160
Ji Tanyin.

532
00:27:00,070 --> 00:27:01,200
Thank you for the pastries.

533
00:27:02,200 --> 00:27:03,240
Rest well.

534
00:27:21,680 --> 00:27:22,790
You're not angry anymore?

535
00:27:24,350 --> 00:27:26,270
When was I ever angry?

536
00:27:29,070 --> 00:27:31,200
Miss Ji, we meet again.

537
00:27:31,590 --> 00:27:32,510
Come on in.

538
00:27:32,510 --> 00:27:33,440
I'll treat you to a meal.

539
00:27:37,720 --> 00:27:39,270
These are all specialties of our small restaurant.

540
00:27:39,270 --> 00:27:40,830
Dear guests, please enjoy your meal.

541
00:27:42,920 --> 00:27:43,720
How do you like these?

542
00:27:43,750 --> 00:27:44,640
If you want to eat

543
00:27:44,640 --> 00:27:45,200
or drink something else,

544
00:27:45,200 --> 00:27:45,830
feel free to order.

545
00:27:45,830 --> 00:27:47,110
It's my treat today anyway.

546
00:27:47,550 --> 00:27:48,830
Thank you, Mei Shan.

547
00:27:49,590 --> 00:27:50,880
Don't mention it, Miss Ji.

548
00:27:50,960 --> 00:27:52,440
Well, one is my long-time old friend,

549
00:27:52,440 --> 00:27:54,240
and the other is someone who bore heavenly thunder together with me.

550
00:27:54,680 --> 00:27:56,240
A meal together is no big deal.

551
00:27:56,960 --> 00:27:58,310
Is this the first time

552
00:27:58,310 --> 00:28:00,000
you've been away from Baitou Mountain all these years?

553
00:28:00,240 --> 00:28:01,030
Yes, indeed.

554
00:28:01,590 --> 00:28:02,350
I've only stayed in the mountain

555
00:28:02,350 --> 00:28:03,920
for a mere few decades.

556
00:28:03,920 --> 00:28:05,070
I never expected the Mortal Realm

557
00:28:05,070 --> 00:28:07,000
to have changed so much.

558
00:28:08,680 --> 00:28:10,030
Come on, let's eat first,

559
00:28:10,030 --> 00:28:10,920
to fill our stomachs a bit.

560
00:28:10,920 --> 00:28:11,510
Today,

561
00:28:11,510 --> 00:28:13,240
I've also invited another friend.

562
00:28:13,440 --> 00:28:14,270
What friend?

563
00:28:14,410 --> 00:28:15,690
You'll see when he arrives.

564
00:28:21,400 --> 00:28:23,070
Look. Since you're trying this dish first,

565
00:28:23,070 --> 00:28:24,750
it's easy to tell you're not a local.

566
00:28:24,790 --> 00:28:26,680
This pouch pancake is the essence

567
00:28:26,680 --> 00:28:28,070
of this table's fare.

