00:28:28,350 --> 00:28:29,240
As for this pouch pancake,

569
00:28:29,240 --> 00:28:31,070
locals call it "sack pancake."

570
00:28:31,240 --> 00:28:32,030
Since it's a "sack,"

571
00:28:32,150 --> 00:28:34,480
you have to fill it with vegetables.

572
00:28:35,240 --> 00:28:36,030
Like this.

573
00:28:37,590 --> 00:28:38,590
That's how it's best eaten.

574
00:28:50,310 --> 00:28:51,110
Here you go.

575
00:28:51,310 --> 00:28:52,110
Thank you.

576
00:28:59,000 --> 00:28:59,790
It tastes really good.

577
00:28:59,880 --> 00:29:01,790
Miss Ji, you're truly appreciative.

578
00:29:01,790 --> 00:29:03,160
No wonder Yuanzhong likes you.

579
00:29:08,790 --> 00:29:10,960
Here, let me show you something interesting.

580
00:29:12,590 --> 00:29:13,240
I bought this yesterday

581
00:29:13,240 --> 00:29:14,680
when I was at the market.

582
00:29:14,680 --> 00:29:15,550
This paper crane

583
00:29:15,550 --> 00:29:17,830
can fly without any magic skills.

584
00:29:18,000 --> 00:29:19,400
Besides, it's coated with Tung Oil,

585
00:29:19,400 --> 00:29:20,680
so it won't get wet in the rain.

586
00:29:20,920 --> 00:29:21,640
Isn't it amazing?

587
00:29:21,640 --> 00:29:23,110
There's a piece of iron inside.

588
00:29:23,350 --> 00:29:24,680
When the iron piece rotates,

589
00:29:25,000 --> 00:29:26,310
it has an energy-storing effect.

590
00:29:26,310 --> 00:29:27,200
When the energy is released,

591
00:29:27,200 --> 00:29:27,830
it should be able to make

592
00:29:27,830 --> 00:29:28,880
the wings of this paper crane

593
00:29:28,880 --> 00:29:29,880
flap up and down.

594
00:29:29,920 --> 00:29:31,640
However, it should only work once.

595
00:29:31,640 --> 00:29:32,400
That's right.

596
00:29:32,790 --> 00:29:33,750
The merchant who sold it to me

597
00:29:33,750 --> 00:29:34,920
said the same thing.

598
00:29:37,510 --> 00:29:38,590
On my way into the city,

599
00:29:38,680 --> 00:29:39,790
in the mountains on the outskirts,

600
00:29:39,790 --> 00:29:41,400
I saw a huge stone tower.

601
00:29:41,400 --> 00:29:42,640
Black smoke was billowing from inside.

602
00:29:42,640 --> 00:29:43,960
Do you know what it is?

603
00:29:43,960 --> 00:29:45,070
We saw it on our way

604
00:29:45,070 --> 00:29:46,030
into the city as well.

605
00:29:46,030 --> 00:29:46,640
But we only

606
00:29:46,640 --> 00:29:47,830
caught a glimpse from afar.

607
00:29:48,240 --> 00:29:50,790
Is that some kind of workshop?

608
00:29:51,510 --> 00:29:53,110
That's a metallurgy workshop.

609
00:29:53,350 --> 00:29:54,680
It operates non-stop day and night,

610
00:29:54,680 --> 00:29:56,590
and there are many mines around it.

611
00:29:56,590 --> 00:29:58,030
They're all dug very deep.

612
00:29:58,070 --> 00:29:59,590
But those who are mining the mines

613
00:29:59,590 --> 00:30:00,590
are not humans.

614
00:30:00,590 --> 00:30:01,480
Instead, they are

615
00:30:01,500 --> 00:30:02,880
high-hanging iron hammers

616
00:30:02,880 --> 00:30:04,440
and constantly spinning iron shovels.

617
00:30:05,400 --> 00:30:06,510
I heard them call it

618
00:30:06,510 --> 00:30:08,400
the Thunderbolt Device.

619
00:30:09,310 --> 00:30:10,070
When we have the opportunity,

620
00:30:10,070 --> 00:30:11,200
we can go take a look.

621
00:30:12,050 --> 00:30:13,570
Have you been to the south of the city?

622
00:30:13,600 --> 00:30:14,680
That's currently

623
00:30:14,750 --> 00:30:16,270
the most prosperous area of Yandu.

624
00:30:16,440 --> 00:30:17,680
People there travel

625
00:30:17,720 --> 00:30:18,880
by stepping on a kind of

626
00:30:19,350 --> 00:30:21,440
small wooden board with two wheels,

627
00:30:21,510 --> 00:30:22,590
moving freely back and forth.

628
00:30:22,590 --> 00:30:24,400
It's even more convenient than using magic skills.

629
00:30:24,920 --> 00:30:26,440
On the eaves of many houses,

630
00:30:26,440 --> 00:30:28,510
there hangs a kind of huge black umbrella.

631
00:30:28,510 --> 00:30:29,550
It's said that those black umbrellas

632
00:30:29,550 --> 00:30:30,240
can collect

633
00:30:30,240 --> 00:30:31,550
heat from the sun

634
00:30:31,550 --> 00:30:32,720
to keep people warm.

635
00:30:33,480 --> 00:30:35,520
Wood and minerals are both limited resources,

636
00:30:35,590 --> 00:30:36,830
and when they burn,

637
00:30:36,900 --> 00:30:38,080
they release strange odors.

638
00:30:38,110 --> 00:30:39,070
I didn't expect

639
00:30:39,070 --> 00:30:40,550
them to start

640
00:30:40,550 --> 00:30:41,720
looking for alternatives so soon.

641
00:30:41,720 --> 00:30:42,310
Focus on eating.

642
00:30:42,310 --> 00:30:43,000
Indeed.

643
00:30:43,400 --> 00:30:45,070
It's truly a case of one day in the mountains,

644
00:30:45,090 --> 00:30:46,660
a thousand years in the world.

645
00:30:46,790 --> 00:30:47,880
Thanks to craftsmanship,

646
00:30:47,880 --> 00:30:48,920
now ordinary families

647
00:30:48,920 --> 00:30:50,590
can also live a good life.

648
00:30:51,110 --> 00:30:53,350
Compared to magic skills which depend more on innate talent,

649
00:30:53,370 --> 00:30:56,520
craftsmanship truly benefits all living beings.

650
00:30:56,700 --> 00:30:58,780
That Goddess Wushuang

651
00:30:58,800 --> 00:30:59,930
who's worshipped by the human race

652
00:31:00,020 --> 00:31:01,540
truly has immeasurable merits.

653
00:31:06,400 --> 00:31:07,200
Mr. Qi.

654
00:31:07,400 --> 00:31:08,440
It's Mr. Qi.

655
00:31:08,680 --> 00:31:09,720
Why is he here today?

656
00:31:09,720 --> 00:31:10,790
Mr. Qi?

657
00:31:12,240 --> 00:31:12,960
What?

658
00:31:12,960 --> 00:31:14,000
You... You know him?

659
00:31:14,000 --> 00:31:15,160
I've bought his paintings before.

660
00:31:16,110 --> 00:31:17,270
What a coincidence.

661
00:31:18,830 --> 00:31:19,640
Mr. Qi!

662
00:31:19,940 --> 00:31:20,740
Mr. Qi!

663
00:31:23,590 --> 00:31:25,790
Fu. Fu!

664
00:31:26,070 --> 00:31:26,880
Over here.

665
00:31:28,270 --> 00:31:30,110
How dashing.

666
00:31:34,240 --> 00:31:35,030
Come on.

667
00:31:35,050 --> 00:31:36,530
Let me introduce you to two good friends of mine.

668
00:31:38,160 --> 00:31:39,310
This is Fu,

669
00:31:39,330 --> 00:31:40,240
Fu Jiuyun.

670
00:31:41,000 --> 00:31:42,240
I met him on my way

671
00:31:42,240 --> 00:31:42,790
to Yandu.

672
00:31:42,790 --> 00:31:44,030
We've shared a table and had drinks together a few times.

673
00:31:44,030 --> 00:31:46,110
He's a man of refined taste.

674
00:31:46,240 --> 00:31:47,200
I wouldn't say refined.

675
00:31:47,200 --> 00:31:48,270
At most, it's just

676
00:31:48,440 --> 00:31:49,350
a way to entertain myself

677
00:31:49,350 --> 00:31:50,550
when I'm bored and free.

678
00:31:52,000 --> 00:31:52,920
This is Yuanzhong,

679
00:31:52,920 --> 00:31:54,160
a good friend of mine for many years.

680
00:31:54,510 --> 00:31:56,510
This is Miss Ji, Ji Tanyin.

681
00:31:56,510 --> 00:31:57,640
She's skilled in craftsmanship.

682
00:31:57,640 --> 00:31:58,640
I'm not exaggerating.

683
00:31:58,640 --> 00:32:00,200
Her skills are definitely among the best

684
00:32:00,200 --> 00:32:02,070
in Yandu.

685
00:32:03,410 --> 00:32:04,570
Ji Tanyin, right?

686
00:32:05,550 --> 00:32:06,680
What a beautiful name.

687
00:32:08,440 --> 00:32:09,240
Miss Ji.

688
00:32:09,730 --> 00:32:11,450
I am Fu Jiuyun,

689
00:32:11,480 --> 00:32:12,650
a painter.

690
00:32:12,790 --> 00:32:14,750
I live alone here in Yandu,

691
00:32:14,750 --> 00:32:16,350
without family, a wife, or children.

692
00:32:16,400 --> 00:32:17,830
Are you a craftsman, Miss Ji?

693
00:32:18,000 --> 00:32:19,880
To earn Mei Shan's praise,

694
00:32:19,900 --> 00:32:22,900
you must be highly skilled.

695
00:32:23,110 --> 00:32:23,920
As it happens,

696
00:32:23,940 --> 00:32:25,070
I'm recently

697
00:32:25,160 --> 00:32:27,000
quite interested in craftsmanship.

698
00:32:27,310 --> 00:32:29,310
I wonder if I might have the opportunity

699
00:32:29,310 --> 00:32:30,680
to visit you and seek your guidance?

700
00:32:34,270 --> 00:32:35,310
Fu. Fu.

701
00:32:35,310 --> 00:32:36,240
Come on, have a seat first.

702
00:32:36,240 --> 00:32:36,830
Have some wine.

703
00:32:36,830 --> 00:32:37,720
The wine here is quite good.

704
00:32:37,720 --> 00:32:38,750
It's refreshing and not too strong.

705
00:32:38,750 --> 00:32:40,000
Here, let me pour you some.

706
00:32:42,510 --> 00:32:43,790
Is your name Fu Jiuyun?

707
00:32:44,160 --> 00:32:44,960
That's correct.

708
00:32:45,200 --> 00:32:46,440
But the people downstairs just now

709
00:32:46,440 --> 00:32:47,750
all called you Mr. Qi.

710
00:32:47,750 --> 00:32:48,590
I've mentioned that

711
00:32:48,640 --> 00:32:49,790
I'm a painter.

712
00:32:50,000 --> 00:32:50,680
So this name

713
00:32:50,680 --> 00:32:51,960
is somewhat inconvenient.

714
00:32:51,960 --> 00:32:52,750
But of course,

715
00:32:53,000 --> 00:32:54,480
you can call me

716
00:32:54,690 --> 00:32:55,520
whatever you like, Miss.

717
00:32:55,550 --> 00:32:56,440
I bought a treasure basin

718
00:32:56,440 --> 00:32:57,750
from Qiju Pavilion before.

719
00:32:58,200 --> 00:33:00,270
The fish in the painting come to life when they encounter water,

720
00:33:00,640 --> 00:33:02,070
and return to being a painting when the water dries up.

721
00:33:02,550 --> 00:33:03,400
Mr. Xu, the shopkeeper, said

722
00:33:03,400 --> 00:33:04,960
it was Mr. Qi's work.

723
00:33:04,960 --> 00:33:07,640
You're referring to that painting of the swimming fish, right?

724
00:33:07,920 --> 00:33:08,720
That's right.

725
00:33:08,910 --> 00:33:10,150
Indeed, it was my creation.

726
00:33:10,720 --> 00:33:11,830
I didn't expect Mr. Xu

727
00:33:11,830 --> 00:33:12,830
to have sold that painting

728
00:33:12,830 --> 00:33:14,000
to you, Miss.

729
00:33:14,200 --> 00:33:15,270
In that case,

730
00:33:15,640 --> 00:33:17,160
we must be destined to meet.

731
00:33:17,750 --> 00:33:18,880
If you like it,

732
00:33:18,880 --> 00:33:20,960
I can give you a few more as gifts.

733
00:33:20,960 --> 00:33:22,880
I have many such paintings at my residence.

734
00:33:23,070 --> 00:33:24,110
Paintings of birds, beasts,

735
00:33:24,110 --> 00:33:26,030
court ladies, flowers, and plants–I have them all.

736
00:33:26,030 --> 00:33:27,110
If you have time, Miss,

737
00:33:27,200 --> 00:33:29,590
you're welcome to come and appreciate them at my place.

738
00:33:32,960 --> 00:33:33,750
Fu.

739
00:33:33,780 --> 00:33:35,690
Come on, let's drink.

740
00:33:39,880 --> 00:33:40,680
These past few days,

741
00:33:40,700 --> 00:33:42,390
the weather has suddenly become hot,

742
00:33:42,420 --> 00:33:43,180
hasn't it?

743
00:33:43,720 --> 00:33:44,510
Isn't it weird?

744
00:33:45,240 --> 00:33:46,030
Good wine.

745
00:33:47,160 --> 00:33:47,960
Fine wine,

746
00:33:48,750 --> 00:33:49,550
beautiful scenery,

747
00:33:50,480 --> 00:33:51,790
with a beauty by my side.

748
00:33:52,070 --> 00:33:52,880
Mei Shan.

749
00:33:53,200 --> 00:33:54,680
Knowing you as a friend

750
00:33:54,700 --> 00:33:55,940
is the greatest blessing

751
00:33:55,990 --> 00:33:57,560
of my life.

752
00:33:59,270 --> 00:34:00,440
Who would say otherwise?

753
00:34:00,640 --> 00:34:01,880
Come on, let me introduce you to

754
00:34:01,880 --> 00:34:02,750
this other friend of mine.

755
00:34:02,750 --> 00:34:04,110
I didn't introduce him properly earlier

756
00:34:04,110 --> 00:34:05,830
because I was afraid it might frighten you.

757
00:34:05,980 --> 00:34:07,430
This one is quite formidable.

758
00:34:07,510 --> 00:34:08,840
He's the nemesis of the War Demon

759
00:34:08,840 --> 00:34:10,670
and the pillar of the Youhu Clan,

760
00:34:10,670 --> 00:34:11,880
who broke through Pinghu Xianzhou

761
00:34:11,880 --> 00:34:13,000
with just one palm strike,

762
00:34:13,000 --> 00:34:13,920
the last remaining

763
00:34:13,920 --> 00:34:15,190
god in this world,

764
00:34:15,280 --> 00:34:17,360
Yuanzhong, the High Priest of the Youhu Clan.

765
00:34:17,550 --> 00:34:18,440
Impressive, isn't it?

766
00:34:18,460 --> 00:34:20,500
This one is actually his handmaiden.

767
00:34:20,630 --> 00:34:22,510
They are... You know.

768
00:34:22,510 --> 00:34:23,630
That kind of relationship.

769
00:34:24,230 --> 00:34:25,830
The owner of the Divine Left Hand,

770
00:34:26,510 --> 00:34:27,760
High Priest Yuanzhong.

771
00:34:28,040 --> 00:34:29,560
My apologies, my apologies.

772
00:34:30,230 --> 00:34:31,840
However, after the war between gods and demons,

773
00:34:31,960 --> 00:34:32,800
no god has set foot again

774
00:34:32,800 --> 00:34:34,760
in this mortal world.

775
00:34:36,070 --> 00:34:36,920
So, as for

776
00:34:36,920 --> 00:34:38,840
the claim of being the last god in the world,

777
00:34:39,400 --> 00:34:41,880
High Priest, do you agree?

778
00:34:41,960 --> 00:34:43,880
Is that painting in the dance house your work?

779
00:34:44,630 --> 00:34:45,440
Painting?

780
00:34:45,880 --> 00:34:46,800
The Goddess Painting.

781
00:34:49,920 --> 00:34:51,440
The figure in that Goddess Painting

782
00:34:51,760 --> 00:34:52,800
looks a lot like me.

783
00:34:53,550 --> 00:34:54,840
Have you seen me before?

784
00:34:55,690 --> 00:34:56,730
Not exactly.

785
00:34:56,840 --> 00:34:58,360
What do you mean by "not exactly"?

786
00:34:58,800 --> 00:34:59,590
I mean

787
00:35:00,280 --> 00:35:02,030
we have never met in this world

788
00:35:02,230 --> 00:35:03,800
with these appearances.

789
00:35:08,110 --> 00:35:09,840
But I have seen you in my dreams,

790
00:35:11,800 --> 00:35:13,000
more than once.

791
00:35:16,230 --> 00:35:17,320
I wonder, Miss Ji,

792
00:35:17,800 --> 00:35:19,280
have you ever seen me in your dreams?

793
00:35:20,920 --> 00:35:22,710
Yuanzhong! Yuanzhong!

794
00:35:24,480 --> 00:35:26,280
Yuanzhong! Yuan... Yuanzhong!

795
00:35:31,400 --> 00:35:32,150
It seems someone here

796
00:35:32,150 --> 00:35:33,150
doesn't fancy my presence.

797
00:35:33,590 --> 00:35:34,400
Then I won't

798
00:35:34,960 --> 00:35:36,690
disturb your pleasant gathering any longer.

799
00:35:37,510 --> 00:35:38,320
Mei Shan,

800
00:35:39,670 --> 00:35:40,800
thank you for the invitation.

801
00:35:40,840 --> 00:35:42,360
Let's meet some other day.

802
00:35:42,760 --> 00:35:43,550
Miss Ji,

803
00:35:44,480 --> 00:35:45,400
until we meet again.

804
00:35:53,280 --> 00:35:54,950
I'll... I'll see him out.

805
00:36:02,310 --> 00:36:04,350
This is our shop's signature dish, Wealth Tree.

806
00:36:04,440 --> 00:36:06,070
Esteemed guests, please have a taste.

807
00:36:09,800 --> 00:36:10,590
Xiu.

808
00:36:10,670 --> 00:36:11,760
This isn't a gold bean.

809
00:36:11,760 --> 00:36:12,800
You can't eat it.

810
00:36:17,230 --> 00:36:18,360
What are you grunting about?

811
00:36:23,070 --> 00:36:24,150
Scholars and literati

812
00:36:24,150 --> 00:36:26,440
are just so carefree.

813
00:36:27,360 --> 00:36:28,150
Esteemed guests.

814
00:36:28,150 --> 00:36:29,630
There's a letter for Miss Ji.

815
00:36:31,110 --> 00:36:31,830
Don't open it!

816
00:36:33,190 --> 00:36:34,280
Tonight between 7-9 pm,

817
00:36:34,380 --> 00:36:35,530
at Rest Teahouse,

818
00:36:35,840 --> 00:36:37,140
I'd like to invite you there for a chat, beauty.

819
00:36:39,780 --> 00:36:41,570
I... I won't go.

820
00:36:41,840 --> 00:36:42,630
I won't go, either.

821
00:36:54,190 --> 00:36:55,030
Gentleman.

822
00:36:55,480 --> 00:36:56,510
What have you taken a fancy to?

823
00:36:56,800 --> 00:37:00,550
Who made this five-wheel fan?

824
00:37:01,760 --> 00:37:03,440
You have a good eye, Gentleman.

825
00:37:03,440 --> 00:37:04,360
This five-wheel fan

826
00:37:04,360 --> 00:37:06,630
was made by the Zhuang's of our Tongtian Workshop.

827
00:37:06,670 --> 00:37:07,800
Their five-wheel fans

828
00:37:07,800 --> 00:37:09,880
are exquisitely made, sturdy and durable.

829
00:37:09,880 --> 00:37:12,480
One person operating it can cool an entire room.

830
00:37:12,550 --> 00:37:14,920
It's most suitable for summer heat relief.

831
00:37:16,320 --> 00:37:18,590
This isn't Old Zhuang's craftsmanship.

832
00:37:19,400 --> 00:37:20,070
This...

833
00:37:20,960 --> 00:37:22,670
What do you mean by that, Gentleman?

834
00:37:23,000 --> 00:37:25,030
Are you accusing me

835
00:37:25,030 --> 00:37:26,400
of selling fakes?

836
00:37:26,630 --> 00:37:27,710
My Qiju Pavilion

837
00:37:27,920 --> 00:37:29,710
has been operating in Yandu for decades.

838
00:37:29,730 --> 00:37:31,710
What we rely on is honest business practices.

839
00:37:31,710 --> 00:37:32,980
Gentleman, you...

840
00:37:34,030 --> 00:37:35,400
That's not what I meant.

841
00:37:35,920 --> 00:37:37,150
I mean, this five-wheel fan

842
00:37:37,150 --> 00:37:38,440
has been modified by someone else.

843
00:37:38,840 --> 00:37:39,840
That person modified the connection point

844
00:37:39,840 --> 00:37:41,440
between the chain and the axle,

845
00:37:41,510 --> 00:37:42,920
making it easier to operate

846
00:37:42,960 --> 00:37:44,550
and increasing the wind power.

847
00:37:45,230 --> 00:37:46,960
Old Zhuang's craftsmanship is indeed exceptional,

848
00:37:46,960 --> 00:37:48,360
but he's not good at innovation.

849
00:37:49,110 --> 00:37:50,960
So this five-wheel fan

850
00:37:52,030 --> 00:37:54,240
can no longer be considered his work.

851
00:37:55,230 --> 00:37:56,320
I see.

852
00:37:58,030 --> 00:37:59,200
I misunderstood.

853
00:38:02,230 --> 00:38:04,150
Someone gave this to me.

854
00:38:04,880 --> 00:38:06,320
If I'm not mistaken,

855
00:38:07,400 --> 00:38:08,860
these two items

856
00:38:12,330 --> 00:38:14,920
should be crafted by the same person, right?

857
00:38:17,000 --> 00:38:19,630
Your discernment is truly impressive, Gentleman.

858
00:38:19,760 --> 00:38:22,030
These are indeed made by the same person.

859
00:38:22,110 --> 00:38:23,110
Who is this person?

860
00:38:23,110 --> 00:38:23,840
Well...

861
00:38:23,840 --> 00:38:25,070
Where does this person live?

862
00:38:25,070 --> 00:38:26,480
I only know it's a

863
00:38:26,480 --> 00:38:28,280
young woman surnamed Ji.

864
00:38:28,400 --> 00:38:29,820
As for where she lives specifically,

865
00:38:29,880 --> 00:38:30,920
I really have no idea.

866
00:38:31,960 --> 00:38:33,920
A young woman?

867
00:38:33,920 --> 00:38:34,710
That's right.

868
00:38:34,840 --> 00:38:36,880
This Miss Ji's craftsmanship is exceptional.

869
00:38:37,590 --> 00:38:38,400
In my opinion,

870
00:38:38,590 --> 00:38:40,630
she's even better

871
00:38:40,630 --> 00:38:42,230
than many famous master craftsmen.

872
00:38:44,920 --> 00:38:45,710
What?

873
00:38:46,030 --> 00:38:48,230
Do you have prejudice against women, Gentleman?

874
00:38:48,630 --> 00:38:49,720
That would be weird.

875
00:38:50,400 --> 00:38:51,400
Here in Yandu,

876
00:38:51,420 --> 00:38:53,820
we don't practice male superiority.

877
00:38:53,880 --> 00:38:55,150
As long as one is educated

878
00:38:55,150 --> 00:38:56,150
and has learned a craft,

879
00:38:56,150 --> 00:38:57,030
regardless of gender,

880
00:38:57,030 --> 00:38:59,000
they can make a living.

881
00:38:59,230 --> 00:39:01,510
After all, the ancestor of our craftsmanship,

882
00:39:01,920 --> 00:39:03,230
Goddess Wushuang,

883
00:39:03,550 --> 00:39:06,190
was also a woman.

884
00:39:06,600 --> 00:39:08,250
You've misunderstood, Sir.

885
00:39:09,440 --> 00:39:10,760
I'm just curious

886
00:39:11,220 --> 00:39:13,340
how such a young lady

887
00:39:13,370 --> 00:39:15,160
could have such remarkable skills.

888
00:39:16,630 --> 00:39:19,070
It's truly a case of the new generation surpassing the old,

889
00:39:19,230 --> 00:39:22,710
and the young outshining their predecessors.

890
00:39:23,360 --> 00:39:25,150
In that case, I apologize for my rudeness.

891
00:39:25,960 --> 00:39:26,800
Sir.

892
00:39:28,510 --> 00:39:30,590
If that young lady comes to your shop again,

893
00:39:31,000 --> 00:39:32,480
please keep her here.

894
00:39:33,070 --> 00:39:33,880
This...

895
00:39:34,030 --> 00:39:36,120
Just tell her someone admires her craftsmanship

896
00:39:36,250 --> 00:39:38,120
and wishes to meet her.

897
00:39:38,630 --> 00:39:39,590
That won't be difficult.

898
00:39:39,920 --> 00:39:41,280
Miss Ji comes to my shop

899
00:39:41,280 --> 00:39:42,800
every few days.

900
00:39:43,110 --> 00:39:43,960
However, I don't know

901
00:39:43,960 --> 00:39:45,510
where you live, Gentleman.

902
00:39:45,510 --> 00:39:46,670
If she comes,

903
00:39:46,710 --> 00:39:48,420
how should I find you?

904
00:39:48,450 --> 00:39:51,220
Just come find me at Master Yan's Mansion.

905
00:39:51,480 --> 00:39:52,440
Master Yan's Mansion?

906
00:39:53,320 --> 00:39:56,510
Guan Zhi, Master Yan's Mansion.

907
00:39:57,740 --> 00:40:00,010
Yan... Master Yan?

908
00:40:22,030 --> 00:40:23,000
What are you thinking about?

909
00:40:24,400 --> 00:40:25,090
You're here.

910
00:40:25,110 --> 00:40:26,400
You didn't hear me knocking just now,

911
00:40:26,510 --> 00:40:27,800
so I came in directly.

912
00:40:30,880 --> 00:40:32,070
That guy's identity is suspicious.

913
00:40:32,190 --> 00:40:33,440
You're not allowed to meet him.

914
00:40:35,110 --> 00:40:35,920
I won't go.

915
00:40:36,030 --> 00:40:37,440
If you run into him outside,

916
00:40:37,710 --> 00:40:38,960
you're not allowed to talk to him either.

917
00:40:39,800 --> 00:40:40,960
If he speaks to me,

918
00:40:40,960 --> 00:40:42,400
am I not allowed to respond?

919
00:40:44,880 --> 00:40:46,070
I won't talk to him.

920
00:40:48,480 --> 00:40:49,960
Let's go eat.

921
00:40:50,590 --> 00:40:51,550
I'm not going.

922
00:40:54,320 --> 00:40:55,110
Why?

923
00:40:55,510 --> 00:40:56,360
I'm not hungry yet.

924
00:41:12,550 --> 00:41:13,280
What's this for?

925
00:41:13,280 --> 00:41:14,400
I'll go wash Xiu's feet.

926
00:41:16,680 --> 00:41:17,470
Wash his feet?

927
00:42:09,150 --> 00:42:13,710
[Ningrui Pavilion]
